          span[aria-hidden="true"]
            | ×
      .modal-body
        .text-body
          .body-title
            h3.title.text-center
              | ARTYQUE For Artists
            br
            h4.color.c-blue.modal-lead-text
              | ARTYQUE is a new kind of agency dedicated to the career growth of emerging and mid-career artists across Europe. 
          .container-fluid.separate-content-bottom.c-medium.text-justify
            .row.mb-4
              .col-12.col-sm-6
                | Acting on your behalf and only in your interest, we promote your work and organise your exhibitions across Europe, find fundings for your projects, develop your provenance, and ultimately increase the value of your works. Simply put, we are here to support your success, believe in your talent and become your ally. 
                br
                br
              .col-12.col-sm-6
                |  After signing with us you will get a personal agent with whom you will develop your digital portfolio on our website. We will then work our magic while you enjoy a stress-free creation process back to your studio.
              .col-12.text-center
                h4.color.c-blue.modal-lead-text.mt-3
                  | Your only task will be creating your next masterpiece.
                br
      .container-bullets
