          ul
            li
              |  Promote your portfolio to galleries and art institutions that fit your talent
            li
              |  Organise new shows of your works in Europe
            li
              |  Increase your press visibility
            li
              |  Connect you with collectors and patrons
            li
              |  Support your career growth 
      .text-body.text-center.separate-content
        .body-title
          h3.text-center.modal-lead-text
            | What is your wildest dream as an Artist? Let us bring you one step closer
          h4.c-blue
            | Send us your portfolio at info@artyque.com and let's <br> schedule an interview. 
        = link_to "Contact Us", contact_path, class: "button-primary"
